{"tid":886095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劫胸圍打底褲 青年囚28月","createTime":"2018-11-02T00:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T01:41:22.000Z","uid":65433,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad139e03d9f7b7dc4c4fd500c7c4f209af32ba5b","tid":886095,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:34:52.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】<span style=\"color: red;\">38歲夜歸女子</span>返家途中遭青年尾隨施襲，對方劫財不成，遂<span style=\"color: red;\">要求她交出胸圍和打底褲</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">又問她「我已沒有拍拖3年，你可不可以做我女朋友」</span>。該青年昨在區域法院承認搶劫，被判囚28個月。<br />\n<br />\n　3次非禮案底 父是現役警員<br />\n<br />\n　辯方求情時透露，被告劉朗彥（<span style=\"color: red;\">25歲</span>）的父親是現役警員，被告之前已有3次非禮案底。控方案情指事主於去年12月12日凌晨2時半獨自回家，經過鯉魚門廣場的便利店時，目睹被告盯着她，行經被告時遭被告從後箍頸及用拳打頭，繼而將她拖到附近一幢樓宇的緊急出口。事主當時嗅到被告身上有酒氣。<br />\n<br />\n　被告後來要求事主交出銀包和錢，並在事主向他表示無帶錢後，將她推倒在地及繼續打頭，事主的後腦更曾撞在地上。事主曾向被告說，即使打死她亦無意義，被告遂要求事主除去及交出她的打底褲，事主問是否交出打底褲後便讓她離開，被告答應。接着，被告又要求事主交出胸圍。<br />\n<br />\n　被告待事主交出打底褲和胸圍後，曾問事主：「我已沒有拍拖3年，你可不可以做我女朋友？」事主沒有回應，被告手執事主的胸圍和打底褲最終離去。事主臉上感到痛楚及後腦流血，坐在地上約10分鐘後被途人發現及報警。經治療後，事主頭部需縫3針。<br />\n<br />\n　警方最終透過附近屋苑的閉路電視，發現被告手執紅色胸圍進入大廈，稍後將他拘捕。被告在警誡下稱，因事主「搞」他，故毆打事主，亦無對事主做其他事。<br />\n<br />\n　【案件編號：DCCC179/18】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個熟女真係咁正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae4e67c6711689e1e5787facee4494e178cf906","tid":886095,"uid":67908,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T00:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/02/084548_9b35a47c34ad70b31b130df74cf8a43f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F02%2F084548_9b35a47c34ad70b31b130df74cf8a43f.jpg&h=fb557775&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22b76b52c798fdaefcff55ecb1abc608f33b8d3d","tid":886095,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"終於有單判得正常啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c4b863bd9d5ae981c26aacbdda9b0c09658d82","tid":886095,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b76b52c798fdaefcff55ecb1abc608f33b8d3d","tid":886095,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"終於有單判得正常啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"又無學歷屋企又無錢 差唔多啦"},{"pid":"f79ae3809c7d5cbf5ef8ec0335cc3b39ea688817","tid":886095,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29c4b863bd9d5ae981c26aacbdda9b0c09658d82","tid":886095,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b76b52c798fdaefcff55ecb1abc608f33b8d3d","tid":886095,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"終於有單判得正常啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"又無學歷屋企又無錢 差唔多啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:12:13.000Z","msg":"佢有警察老豆，但係唔夠高級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec0984328eb813dcbaaafeac3fdc09920542c09","tid":886095,"uid":136662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"發現被告手執紅色胸圍進入大廈<br />\n<br />\n樓下看更唔會覺得奇怪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96047f4c5662dc7b967852506c80614b4c053cf1","tid":886095,"uid":4420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ec0984328eb813dcbaaafeac3fdc09920542c09","tid":886095,"uid":1